<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
</head>

<body>
    <style>
        body {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        body>div {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            min-height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        body>div>pre {
            textAlign: center;
            textAlignLast: left;
            width: 40%;
            display: block;
        }

        body>div>span {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            height: 10%;
            width: 700px;
            background-color: red;
        }
    </style>
    <div>
        <pre>
            Hello, {{this.name}}. We have received a request to reset your password.

            If you really did request that, please click <a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" title="" target="_blank"  href="http://localhost:3003/{{hashCode}}">here</a> to finalize your password reset.

            if you didin't request that, you can just ignore this email. 
            
            Att.

            Web Developer
        </pre>
        <a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" title="" target="_blank" href="http://localhost:3003/{{hashCode}}">
            <span>
                Reset Password
            </span>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>